 TestHitTracking dummy;m
⍝ Test that hit events are recorded in the match hitLog
 ⎕IO←0
 m←##.Engine.Run ##.Rhobots.Spinner ##.Rhobots.Kamikaze
 ⍝ Match should have hitLog
 Assert 'has hitLog' (0≠⎕NC'm.hitLog')
 ⍝ In a Spinner vs Kamikaze match, there should be hits
 Assert 'hitLog not empty' (0<≢m.hitLog)
 ⍝ Each hit event is a 3-element vector: (shooter target damage)
 Assert 'hit event has 3 elements' (3=≢⊃m.hitLog)
 ⍝ Damage should equal bullet damage config
 Assert 'hit damage = config' (##.Cfg.BULLET_DAMAGE=2⊃⊃m.hitLog)
